dcterms:description: The nuScenes dataset comprises 1,000 driving sequences, with 700, 150, and 150 sequences allocated for training, validation, and testing, respectively. Each sequence spans approximately 20 seconds at 20 frames per second (FPS). The dataset provides calibrated vehicle attitude information and bounding box annotations across 10 classes with long-tailed distributions.
dcterms:title: nuScenes
